snippet.title: Version 4.4 "Vibrant Harriers Aloft in Spring Breeze" Trailer | Genshin Impact
snippet.description:
Spring has come early, and in its wake a rising beast, gazing up towards the clouds against an auspicious breeze.
Soaring up like wild cranes the harlequin kites ascend, while a stream flows back through a vale of hidden treasures.
